Package de.linearbits.objectselector.datatypes Description

This package provides datat types for Object Selector.

  • The class DBoolean represents a boolean data type
  • The class DDate represents a date
  • The class DNumeric represents a numeric data type
  • The class DString represents a string
  • The class DataType offers static constants and methods for accessing data types
Author:
Fabian Prasser
